summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to Land Use and Zoning, amending Plats 2W and 2E, Pages 36 and 37 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle (Ordinance 86300) to rezone certain property located on both sides of 24th Avenue N.W. generally between N. W. 77th Street and N.W. 80th Street., from Community Business (BC) Zone to intermediate business (BI) Street.
